{"tid":831492,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人死之後變靈魂長存 同 人死如燈滅 ，邊個概念恐怖啲？","createTime":"2018-09-22T03:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T10:08:50.000Z","uid":90,"like":90,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"cdde42adeca35c22a0d03bba777ed8a5fdee111d","tid":831492,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"長存： 永無盡頭嘅痛苦<br />\n燈滅：失去思考，乜都冇，無盡空虛<br />\n<br />\n感覺以人類嘅角度嚟諗，兩樣都好恐怖"},{"pid":"d0c696825cb1b5e3c46977e00130845ecaf924cf","tid":831492,"uid":142999,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"點解長存喺永無盡嘅痛苦？"},{"pid":"24b05f9aee54fa1c3a94bc6bebc3bf973358b5c4","tid":831492,"uid":184716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"長存"},{"pid":"8aa045c5692bebbaedc481e1f1f613be39b24e56","tid":831492,"uid":90,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"d0c696825cb1b5e3c46977e00130845ecaf924cf","tid":831492,"uid":142999,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:59:21.000Z","msg":"點解長存喺永無盡嘅痛苦？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"因為你個人冇咗終點<br />\n一直存在落去<br />\n感覺會好易悶<br />\n當你體驗晒有意思嘅嘢<br />\n當你完全所有嘅目標<br />\n當你已經唔知做乜好個刻<br />\n感覺會好痛苦<br />\n<br />\n一時三刻整理唔到個原因出嚟<br />\n但當細心一諗就會覺得呢件事好痛苦<br />\n我相信每個人都會喺長存上得到唔同嘅痛苦<br />\n<br />\n當然痛唔痛苦都要睇長存嘅形式"},{"pid":"cdb1d620cdfa770e5ea16e00f50ffd130be36f39","tid":831492,"uid":93855,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"你冇思考就唔知咩係痛苦啦"},{"pid":"2f6af3ee884889b607ef18fd2131cdd6ea33208e","tid":831492,"uid":93855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cdb1d620cdfa770e5ea16e00f50ffd130be36f39","tid":831492,"uid":93855,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:09:06.000Z","msg":"你冇思考就唔知咩係痛苦啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"嘆就唔會覺得空虛"},{"pid":"4c3ae9b3de589a127d80f7361f2de9ea10509c2f","tid":831492,"uid":93855,"like":0,"di